# Beads tracker artifacts (Dolt DB, export state, lock files). The tracker is
# being retired; these are local-only generated artifacts that should never be
# committed (a `git add -A` would otherwise sweep them in).
.beads/dolt/
.beads/export-state/
.beads/*.lock

